==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Confabulation
<hw>Con*fab`u*la"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>confabulatio</ets>.]</ety> <def>Familiar talk; easy, unrestrained,
unceremonious conversation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Friends' <qex>confabulations</qex> are comfortable at all times,
as fire in winter.</q> <rj><qau>Burton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Confabulatory</ent>⟦br⟧
